{"tid":1408532,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［ 緊急！］8月5號朝早！個個都有責任要做！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-04T17:33:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T18:04:16.000Z","uid":238467,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1a3be5af6c4709d2349d31012a190e9e5a9bb33e","tid":1408532,"uid":238467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:33:13.000Z","msg":"就係幫不合作運動前線手足打氣！<br />\n唔好令到佢地孤立！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WTuApPY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWTuApPY.png&h=c68b9cb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我完全明白有好多人同手足無辦法咁方便罷工<br />\n而唔洗擔心 我地係會幫你地罷嘅！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n但係我地做緊野嘅同時<br />\n係需要有人做以下幾樣重要嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一 好似上次嘅不合作運動咁<br />\n一定會有人話我地係做緊同民意相反嘅事<br />\n請各位打工仔同手足請唔好吝嗇你地嘅掌聲同歡呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁班藍絲奴工就會收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二 各位手足 請保持冷靜<br />\n我地做自己野就得 必要時 問下現場有無人支持<br />\n到時就會有第一點嘅人幫手<br />\n盡量避免直接開佢波<br />\n人地開我地波嘅話 咁就識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三 唔係前線嘅手足<br />\n做文宣！！！ 可以大聲播鏗鏘集<br />\n可以大聲播立場 乜都得<br />\n強迫佢地睇 脫離TVB嘅魔爪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 叫大家罷工去七區集會<br />\n返屋企換套衫好 直接去又好<br />\n基本上有齊不反對通知書<br />\n和理非同伴請放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求！！！！！<br />\n缺一不何！！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以幫我推下<br />\n聽日就係喇 想集中下意見<br />\n大家有意見都可以提出討論 <br />\nThank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EW1V78v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEW1V78v.png&h=f3be1ae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望各位幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96798a57a2dc42a42326dd0ead509531764733ba","tid":1408532,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:33:51.000Z","msg":"PUSH <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">8月5 一齊罷工</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊支持下<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d54f45c26573c5f686a7e7437f41b637ba0a87f5","tid":1408532,"uid":238467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:34:08.000Z","msg":"我知我post左幾次<br />\n唔好意思！因為我見熱門太多重複無意義嘅po<br />\n想po多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家聽日做得到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb4f910f971f2e1f57f77eeff85283cff4a606d","tid":1408532,"uid":298077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢度冇人支持你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\"